   "id": "41745d06",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Analyse des animés\n",
    "Chargement, nettoyage et classement des meilleurs animés."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "2620ad02",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Étape 1 : Charger les données"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "41a0a096",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "ename": "",
     "evalue": "
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv('animes.csv')\n",
    "print('Nombre de lignes :', len(df))\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "115c90d3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "## Étape 2 : Nettoyer les données"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "30a9e71c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Remplacer les cellules vides par NaN\n",
    "df.replace('', np.nan, inplace=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Convertir les notes en nombres\n",
    "df['Note_Globale'] = pd.to_numeric(df['Note_Globale'], errors='coerce')\n",
    "df['Nb_Episodes'] = pd.to_numeric(df['Nb_Episodes'], errors='coerce')\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Valeurs manquantes :')\n",
    "print(df[['Note_Globale', 'Nb_Episodes']].isnull().sum())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d04f6a84",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Étape 3 : Supprimer les doublons"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "36259492",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print('Doublons avant :', df.duplicated(subset=['Anime']).sum())\n",
    "\n",
    "df.drop_duplicates(subset=['Anime'], keep='first', inplace=True)\n",
    "df.reset_index(drop=True, inplace=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Doublons après :', df.duplicated(subset=['Anime']).sum())\n",
    "print('Animés restants :', len(df))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "bd838365",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "## Étape 4 : Créer le score final\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "score_final = 0.6 × Note_Globale + 0.4 × popularité\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "La popularité = nombre d épisodes normalisé entre 0 et 10 (avec log pour éviter qu One Piece écrase tout)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "1d3de4cf",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Popularité = Nb épisodes normalisé sur 10\n",
    "df['popularite'] = np.log1p(df['Nb_Episodes'])\n",
    "df['popularite'] = df['popularite'] / df['popularite'].max() * 10\n",
    "\n",
    "# Score final\n",
    "df['score_final'] = 0.6 * df['Note_Globale'] + 0.4 * df['popularite']\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Score calculé !')\n",
    "df[['Anime', 'Note_Globale', 'popularite', 'score_final']].dropna().head(5)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "05e59863",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Étape 5 : Top 10 des meilleurs animés "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "eef942e2",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Garder seulement les animés avec une note\n",
    "df_notes = df.dropna(subset=['Note_Globale'])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Top 10\n",
    "top10 = df_notes.nlargest(10, 'score_final')[['Anime', 'Note_Globale', 'Nb_Episodes', 'score_final']]\n",
    "top10 = top10.round(2).reset_index(drop=True)\n",
    "top10.index += 1\n",
    "\n",
    "top10"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "276249c3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "## Étape 6 : Graphique du Top 10"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "803d72ef",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "plt.barh(top10['Anime'][::-1], top10['score_final'][::-1], color='steelblue')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Score Final')\n",
    "plt.title('🏆 Top 10 des meilleurs animés')\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.savefig('top10.png')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a8560864",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Conclusions\n",
    "\n",
    "- On a chargé **57 animés**, nettoyé les valeurs vides et supprimé les doublons (Baccano! apparaissait deux fois).\n",
    "- Le score final combine la **note de qualité** (60%) et la **popularité via les épisodes** (40%).\n",
    "- **One Piece** arrive souvent en tête grâce à ses 1090 épisodes malgré une note légèrement inférieure aux mieux notés.\n",
    "- Les animés sans note (24 sur 57) ont été exclus faute de données."
   ]
  }
 ],
